entries.femaleVariant: Maybe I'll drop by The Afterlife. See if anythin' beats this grind.
I dunno, choom. I used to man the door to The Afterlife. Saw hundreds like you walk in.
Bright-eyed, game for anythin', ready to bring this city to its knees.
Strolled in like minor fuckin' deities. Know how they walked out?
In the best case – 'thout a flicker of hope left in their eyes. Worst case – in a body bag.
You think you just hook up with a fixer and its easy sailin' from there. But take it from the guy who's seen this shit – you're plain wrong.
Keep your ass put. You wanna live to see the next Bushido sequel, don't you?
